did.abstract: Collection consists of mounted black and white and color reproductions of paintings. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: These materials are stored offsite at the Library Shelving Facility. For access to the materials, please make a request at the Art & Architecture Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Organized alphabetically by country. Further subdivided by individual artist name.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of mounted black and white and color reproductions of paintings. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.
